{"tid":1073673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過海隧道由收費改成免費","createTime":"2019-03-23T00:51:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T06:18:10.000Z","uid":55672,"like":7,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b2d3cd909a8b36903b29894c298ceead24a06fb5","tid":1073673,"uid":55672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T00:51:31.000Z","msg":"政府近排好落力sell三隧分流方案，但支持聲音未去到足以通過落實，一齊停留係磋商階段。<br />\n<br />\n咁岩睇到本港報章一個投稿建議，係現有車輛牌費上加價，例如:現時1500cc車牌費約$4000，再加$18200($35平均過海費 x 2來回 x 260日) = $22200 1500cc 新牌費。但係就免去一年內過隧道費用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n投稿有話最終階段可以抽起唒所有隧道收費站，車輛用少左時間逼係收費站，車輛使用者又可以唔洗再就住隧道收費，自由選擇最方便的過海方法。<br />\n<br />\n牌費增加亦可以將購置車輛的固定成本增加，有望減少本港的車輛數目。<br />\n<br />\n不過可以預期過海次數較少的車主會大力反對建議...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位巴打對呢個建議又有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0716afba388d6947f9eaf530f6cf06dd30cc20","tid":1073673,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T01:00:29.000Z","msg":"塞車位搬去第度＝解決問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fccf34c65eba017ad836590db9074eba3dd608e","tid":1073673,"uid":64318,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T01:01:02.000Z","msg":"仲以為真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1abf41a0b6ce63586a1ede3e8d0623f198ce62d7","tid":1073673,"uid":230703,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T01:03:31.000Z","msg":"打擊唔用隨道的人，反面睇係迫大家多用隨道，真係